            <div class="title">
                Expenditure Arising Out Of The War
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1942-09-09/debates/71824e4d-b8e3-4683-a66a-95d6228e3627/Adjournment" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
