<p class="">I am afraid one cannot deduce it from that.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-de866d8c-2beb-4faf-acb2-81ea8230657c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
